title: Runny
review: I followed directions for coconut yogurt instapot using coconut cream.Twice my batches of yogurt did not work. Thickened on the top but runny on the rest of the quarts. I am disappointed. I don't know if it was the cultures fault, but I'm unable to give it a good rating.
